## 1 · SETUP & FIRST RUN

### 1.1 — Install (DevPod)

```bash
brew install loft-sh/devpod/devpod                                        # macOS
devpod up https://github.com/marcuspat/turbo-flow --ide vscode
```

### 1.2 — Install (Manual)

```bash
git clone https://github.com/marcuspat/turbo-flow -b main
cd turbo-flow/v4
chmod +x .devcontainer/setup-turboflow-4.sh
./.devcontainer/setup-turboflow-4.sh
source ~/.bashrc
turbo-status
```

### 1.3 — Initialize Ruflo in Any Project

```bash
npx ruflo@latest init --wizard
claude mcp add ruflo -- npx -y ruflo@latest mcp start
```

### 1.4 — First Time on a New Project

```bash
# Using TF aliases:
rf-init && bd init && gnx-analyze && hooks-train

# Using native commands:
npx ruflo@latest init && bd init && npx gitnexus analyze && npx ruflo@latest hooks pretrain
```

### 1.5 — Session Boot (Every Session)

```bash
# Using TF aliases:
source ~/.bashrc && rf-doctor && bd ready --json && gnx-analyze && hooks-train && rf-daemon && turbo-status

# Using native commands:
source ~/.bashrc
npx ruflo@latest doctor --fix
bd ready --json
npx gitnexus analyze
npx ruflo@latest hooks pretrain
npx ruflo@latest daemon start
turbo-status
```

