- Isolation Rules: Which contexts get their own worktrees
- Agent Teams Rules: Which agent roles this project needs
- Model Routing: Which parts need Opus vs Sonnet vs Haiku
- GitNexus Checkpoints: Shared code paths where agents MUST check blast radius
- Security Requirements: Project-specific security rules from the ADRs
- Hooks Configuration: Which hooks are active and what they enforce
- Cost Guardrails: Adjust the $15/hr cap if needed
- Stack Reference: Project-specific tools, frameworks, and conventions
```

